data.title: Press Releases
data.text:
Dell Names Marius Haas President of Enterprise Solutions

Dell today announced that Marius Haas, a 20-year industry veteran, has joined the company as president of Enterprise Solutions.

Dell Helps Customers Modernize Their IT Environments With Closing Of Make Technologies Acquisition

Dell announced today it has finalized the acquisition of Make Technologies, a leading application modernization software and services company.

Dell Reports First Quarter Financial Results

Dell announced its fiscal 2013 first quarter results today, continuing to show progress in its move to being a total enterprise services and solutions provider.

Dell Completes Acquisition of IT Security Leader SonicWALL

Dell today announced it has finalized its acquisition of SonicWALL, Inc., a leader in advanced network security, secure remote access, email security, backup and recovery, and management and reporting.

Dell Announces Intent to Acquire Wyse Technology

Dell today announced it has signed a definitive agreement to acquire Wyse Technology, the global leader in cloud client computing, to significantly extend its desktop virtualization offerings.

Dell Announces Intent to Acquire SonicWALL, Inc.

Dell today announced it has signed a definitive agreement to acquire SonicWALL, Inc., a leader in advanced network security and data protection.

Dell Acquires AppAssure

Dell Inc. (NASDAQ: DELL) today announced it has acquired AppAssure, a global leader in complete application protection for virtual, physical and cloud infrastructures.

Dell Record Fiscal Year 2012 Highlighted By Enterprise Solutions and Services Strength

Dell’s further expansion as an enterprise solutions and services provider highlighted the company’s most successful financial year ever.
